Class MassMavenizerMojo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
      • io.github.fastcube.factory.tibco.bw.maven.source.AbstractProjectsListMojo
        • io.github.fastcube.factory.tibco.bw.maven.source.ExistingBWProjectsListMojo
          • io.github.fastcube.factory.tibco.bw.maven.source.MassMavenizerMojo
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ContextEnabled, Mojo

    @Mojo(name="mavenize-bw-projects",
      requiresProject=false)
public class MassMavenizerMojo
extends ExistingBWProjectsListMojo

    This goal "mavenizes" a list of existing TIBCO BusinessWorks projects.
    The Mavenizer is the default "Mavenizer Archetype" (archetype-bw-mavenizer).

    Refer to bw:list-bw-projects goal for an explanation about projects lists.

    Author:
    Radwane Mabchour
